WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome to Introduction to SQL.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:10.000
SQL stands for Structured Query Language.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:15.000
SQL is used to manage and interact with relational databases.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Databases store information in tables, rows, and columns.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.900
SQL helps retrieve, insert, update, and delete data efficiently.
